auto configure vg setting current for ubuntu12.04

get_ip.py
usage: python ./get_ip.py

conn_vg.py
usage: python ./conn_vg.py ip port


examples:
	1. use get_ip.py to get server ip and save it in tmp.txt file with [ping, ip] format, meanwhile get port number in tmp.html file with specified ip address(you may need to use a proxy 127.0.0.1:8087 to get it work):
	python ./get_ip.py

	2. apply setttings or restore default settings:
	add settings:	python ./conn_vg.py 27.1.128.141 995 1
	remove settings	python ./conn_vg.py 27.1.128.141 995 0
